long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Does your doge want to browse the internet, meet new friends, or display their creative works but can't read the page? Look no further, we have the solution for you. Cheems Translator changes english directly to cheems without difficult to use workarounds. It works quickly to give your doggos a quick and seamless experience on the internet. 

Improves:
- Reading comprehension 
- Generative AI results
- Boss' crazed emails 

Features:
- Easy install and setup
- Works with dynamic content
- Avoids breaking websites
- No cookies and no data leaves your browser
- Self contained experience
- Open source
- Fun to use with a screen reader!

Code on GitHub: https://www.github.com/Dovencio/Cheems-Translator/

Translator code provided by Miraz Mac: https://mirazmac.com/
